"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-coco-gauff-shared-awesome-moment-with-lebron-james-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"One of the best things about the Olympics is that it brings athletes from so many different sports together and allows some of them to share cool moments with big-name athletes that they will never forget.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what happened to Coco Gauff during Friday's Opening Ceremony when she got to stand alongside LeBron James as the U.S. team's boat traveled past the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9936970023952475, \"rank\": 0.003611019977285152, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis star and NBA legend were the flag bearers for Team USA and the moment was not lost on Gauff.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9974114235101877, \"rank\": 0.0025951733744031323, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5744116920894468, \"rank\": 0.6978247622474381, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This video that she shared on social media is too good:  Coco still can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t believe she is with LeBron James.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u008d\\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fpic.twitter.com/qBioh1aWQW  James and the U.S. men's basketball team kick off their Olympics on Sunday with a showdown against Nikola Jokic and Serbia.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9995156756312334, \"rank\": 0.00037328974492766633, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999767325795141, \"rank\": 1.8287657347929937e-05, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 751, \"title\"